d following the latest EpiDoc guidelines</p>\n             <xi:include href=\"../alists/ISicily-taxonomies.xml\">\n                 <xi:fallback>\n                     <p>Taxonomies for ISicily controlled values</p>\n                 </xi:fallback>\n             </xi:include>\n\t  <xi:include href=\"../alists/charDecl.xml\">\n\t     <xi:fallback>\n\t       <p>ISicily glyphs authority list</p>\n\t     </xi:fallback>\n\t   </xi:include>\n         </encodingDesc>\n        <profileDesc>\n            <calendarDesc>\n                <calendar xml:id=\"julian\">\n                    <p>Julian Calendar</p>\n                </calendar>\n            </calendarDesc>\n            <langUsage>\n                <language ident=\"en\">English</language>\n                <language ident=\"it\">Italian</language>\n                <language ident=\"grc\">Ancient Greek</language>\n                <language ident=\"la\">Latin</language>\n                <language ident=\"he\">Hebrew</language>\n                <language ident=\"phn\">Phoenician</language>\n                <language ident=\"xpu\">Punic</language>\n                <language ident=\"osc\">Oscan</language>\n                <language ident=\"xly\">Elymian</language>\n                <language ident=\"scx\">Sikel</language>\n                <language ident=\"sxc\">Sikan</language>\n            </langUsage>\n            <textClass>\n                <keywords scheme=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins.html\">\n                    <term ana=\"#function.funerary\" ref=\"http://www.eagle-network.eu/voc/typeins/lod/92.html\">funerary</term>\n                </keywords>\n            </textClass>\n        </profileDesc>\n        <revisionDesc status=\"draft\">\n            <listChange>\n                 <change when=\"2018-10-12\" who=\"#JP\">Jonathan Prag created the file based on the publication</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-05\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova normalised Unicode</change>\n            \t   <change when=\"2020-10-08\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova updated list of languages</change>\n            \t\t<change when=\"2020-11-26\" who=\"#SS\">Simona Stoyanova restructured bibliography</change>\n\t    <change when=\"2020-12-21\" who=\"#system\">Updated Zenodo DOI</change>\n            \t<change when=\"2021-01-19\" who=\"#SS\">renumbered files, uris and references</change>\n\t</listChange>\n        </revisionDesc>\n    </teiHeader>\n   <facsimile>\n          <surface type=\"front\">\n            <graphic n=\"screen\" url=\"ISic004382_tiled.tif\" height=\"2016px\" width=\"2717px\">\n                <desc>Photo courtesy of archivio fotografico della soprintendenza di Messina</desc>\n            </graphic>\n              <graphic n=\"print\" url=\"ISic004382.jpg\" height=\"2016px\" width=\"2717px\">\n                  <desc>Photo courtesy of archivio fotografico della soprintendenza di Messina</desc>\n            </graphic>\n        </surface>\n    </facsimile>\n    <text>\n        <body>\n            <div type=\"edition\" xml:space=\"preserve\" xml:lang=\"grc\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <ab>                    \n                    <lb n=\"1\"/>Ῥουφείνα Μαρκία\n                   <lb n=\"2\"/>ζήσασα ἔτη <num value=\"35\">λε</num>\n                    <lb n=\"3\"/>Σόσσις ἀνήρ ἐπόη\n                    <lb n=\"4\" break=\"no\"/>σε ἰδίᾳ γυναικί εὐσεβεσ\n                    <lb n=\"5\" break=\"no\"/>τάτη μνημεῖον\n                </ab>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"apparatus\">\n                <listApp><app><note>Text after Zavettieri 2017 and photograph</note></app>\n                </listApp>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"en\" resp=\"#JP\">\n                <p>Rufina Marcia having lived for 35 years, her husband Sossis made this memorial for his own most pious wife</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"translation\" xml:lang=\"it\" resp=\"Zavettieri\">\n                <p>Rufina Marcia vissuta anni 35, il marito Sossis fece alla propria moglie piissima un monumento</p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"commentary\">\n                <p>Cf. <ref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic003521\">ISic003521</ref> for another female member of the gens Marcia in Messina. The rare name Sossis is also attested at Catania in <ref target=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic001324\">ISic001324</ref></p>\n            </div>\n            <div type=\"bibliography\">\n                <listBibl type=\"edition\">\n                         <bibl>\n                        <author>Zavettieri</author>\n                        <date>2017</date>\n                        <citedRange>169 no.5 fig.5</citedRange>\n                             <ptr target=\"http://zotero.org/groups/382445/items/R9M3U4WX\"/>\n                    <ref target=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001500\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001500</ref></bibl>\n                  </listBibl>\n\t   <listBibl type=\"discussion\"><bibl/></listBibl>\n            </div>\n        </body>\n    </text>\n</TEI>\n",
